'''Hospitality Guides''' were citizens of [[Kegan/Legends|Kegan]] who helped introduce tourists and foreigners to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]. Although Kegan was isolated for several years during the pre-[[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] era, the Hospitality Guides were key in introducing [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]], [[Qui-Gon Jinn/Legends|Qui-Gon Jinn]], [[Siri Tachi/Legends|Siri Tachi]], and [[Adi Gallia/Legends|Adi Gallia]] to the planet of Kegan. There were only two Hospitality Guides: [[V-Haad]] and [[O-Rina]].<ref name="JA">''[[Jedi Apprentice: The Fight for Truth]]''</ref>

